{"tid":910922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【最新】創立匯點 倡議「民主回歸」 接受中共統戰 劉迺強病逝","createTime":"2018-11-21T13:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T14:24:18.000Z","uid":103156,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f4d0815f799a58509a9eb1f90fd10f5ae56b277d","tid":910922,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:36:30.000Z","msg":"【最新】創立匯點 倡議「民主回歸」 接受中共統戰 劉迺強病逝<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181121&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58941760\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181121%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58941760&d=BxbtS97f2HqX%2BhpLIkm3qYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=bdae5fe3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181121%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58941760&h=076c3c30\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181121&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58941760</a>"},{"pid":"36b3f363c18c7b68845a1a092e0d183e46c4b8fd","tid":910922,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:37:19.000Z","msg":"上世紀80年代創立首批民主派政團匯點、倡議「民主回歸」的香港基本法委員會委員劉迺強今晚病逝，終年71歲。前立法會議員、民建聯蔡素玉接受《蘋果》查詢時證實，獲劉迺強友人告知，劉今晚病逝。<br />\n<br />\n蔡素玉指，劉迺強患癌「病咗好耐」，「上次話我哋聽，做咗7、8次化療，又要做手術」，指約三星期前曾與他見面，「當時覺得佢面色差，但仲好樂觀喎，講嘢都登登聲（即大聲），好掛住政事，成日寫網誌，又傳啲文章畀我哋睇」；及至上星期，他未能出席另一次朋友聚會。"},{"pid":"ed4e0d4bb426a919b24a03c182f896b6a4444d6c","tid":910922,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:38:43.000Z","msg":"蔡說劉勇敢面對病魔，「（病情）咁多年惡化、施手術都無數，但佢都好勇敢面對」。對其突然離世感到突然，讚揚對方多年來一直關心香港問題，「對香港好有心」。<br />\n<br />\n2016年全國人大常委會委員長張德江於政府總部會見香港各界人士時，原本站着聽講的劉迺強身體不適，張即着職員找椅子讓劉坐下，更對自己的話太長表示抱歉。張的發言多次因此被打斷，先後慰問劉「沒問題吧？」最終劉在張的發言尾聲由救護員送離現場，張則向劉揮手道別，並叫在場人士掌聲鼓勵身體不適的劉迺強。"},{"pid":"52bd0e15af34aac51af8b07801f9f4609ac144bf","tid":910922,"uid":103156,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WiePqvw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWiePqvw.jpg&h=6af60f7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4204e46b9f4e012248762395fe8953db1ce3d8c8","tid":910922,"uid":66514,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:44:07.000Z","msg":"劉生，rest in peace"},{"pid":"5fe5b2c8db23ba9b73786c4efd10d239604df0f6","tid":910922,"uid":63909,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:44:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢實落地獄</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f35b410c1b424450663c823ac51e7a59d25ee74","tid":910922,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:46:40.000Z","msg":"今年尾咁多人死既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條蛇好惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577a05d92aeb844627eee04a22ebee4532e642c5","tid":910922,"uid":202464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:48:00.000Z","msg":"奶共者。"},{"pid":"27ad9ca3cb18aea6cb4937fa9e9fdea436e2db21","tid":910922,"uid":103156,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WDreBHk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWDreBHk.jpg&h=f13ac1c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基本法委員會委員劉迺強撰文談論特首家人風波，稱「蔡子強之流多行不義必自斃」。(2014/7/7)<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20140707/s00001/1404711433239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20140707%2Fs00001%2F1404711433239&d=BxbtS97f2HqX%2BhpLIkm3qYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=6c620d8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2