2,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:10:41.000Z","msg":"做咗7、8次化療，又要做手術<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80fcb696109e1fe300f0b03346d94e33fdabf91a","tid":910922,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:24:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">劉迺強</span>早年曾在座談會上分享對六四的看法，<span style=\"color: red;\">重申當晚沒有一個學生被坦克輾過、天安門廣場沒有人因鎮壓而死</span>，又指王維林當時有信心，才會站在坦克車前，但強調「當時他沒被輾過」，只因為事件中有人反抗，才難免出現傷亡，並非政府故意射殺手無寸鐵的學生，不應稱事件為「屠城」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1369972/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1369972%2F&d=BxbtS97f2HqX%2BhpLIkm3qYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=8ee625ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1369972%2F&h=41f85843\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1369972/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}